{"tid":1890238,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男獲撤暴動罪兼得訟費成首例 被告：冇特別高興，仲有幾百個手足俾人告","createTime":"2020-02-21T05:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T06:25:45.000Z","uid":127929,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61d847239289ac2a13416c4f1b958ac79018655a","tid":1890238,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"獲撤控的張文偉仍<span style=\"color: red;\">心繫其他被控的手足</span>。<br />\n<br />\n【更新】<br />\n<br />\n網民去年8月在觀塘舉行主題為「燃點香港‧全民覺醒」的遊行，要求政府回應五大訴求，並關注智慧燈柱的私隱問題，最終演變為警民衝突。警方先後拘控三名男子暴動罪。惟案件今再訊時，其中兩人獲撤控兼可獲得訟費，是反送中案中首宗撤暴動罪的案件。其中一名獲撤控的張姓被告於庭外表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然撤控放心咗，但冇特別高興，因為仲有其他幾百個手足俾人告</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n張指當日<span style=\"color: red;\">被制服時曾被警棍「打爆頭」</span>，導致頭部需要縫針。他又透露自己從事零售業，「件案都影響返工，朋友同屋企人都幾擔心」。他指他於日資公司工作，惟擔保期間須要每周六去警署報到，令他不能赴日出差，幸好僱主尚算體諒，「已經算好彩，相比其他手足連工都冇得返」。<br />\n<br />\n被告續指....<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200221/VNBJRSJY5L42CS2XFGB65NU3PM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2FVNBJRSJY5L42CS2XFGB65NU3PM%2F&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVL0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=ea5f1987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200221%2FVNBJRSJY5L42CS2XFGB65NU3PM%2F&h=290cef16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200221/VNBJRSJY5L42CS2XFGB65NU3PM/</a>"},{"pid":"a0237ecb2b807a78c7165acf6ae35ef7abe2e6be","tid":1890238,"uid":785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"控方玩鳩告 浪費手足時間 嚴重影響生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ac4ed7cded4a01e1e3fc4c8f409f070a76ad27","tid":1890238,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"仲有, 今日係721<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fba8PqK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFba8PqK.jpg&h=890f62d1&s